#Write a program that gradually reverses the given string. Read the string from a keyboard using input() function. Suppose if user enters Abid then your program prints:
#bidA
#idAb
#dAbi
#Abid

#Submission: Create Account on github.com and submit assignments over there

Name=input("\nEnter the String !!! ");
print("\nThe name is ",Name);
for i in range(len(Name)):
    Name=Name[1:]+Name[0];
    print(Name)
    
    

